\par Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid4982948\charrsid4982948 (LAUGHS) Yes! It\rquote s quite strong, actually, saying that you felt it was a prison, isn\rquote t it. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 
