\par Judith:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid4982948\charrsid4982948 Yes. Yes. Yeah, you were supposed to make a good 
marriage. And my best friend, called Sue, she was not an academic, she left at 16, after \lquote O\rquote 
 Levels, but she died of cancer about three years ago. I broke up contact with her, but I heard through somebody else, that she was very very bitter. And my sister 
had a reunion with some of our contemporaries. ... I think my sister, she gave up her very promising career, she got her Ph.D. before me, she joint wrote a standard textbook for zoology, for schools, and then she, you know, gave it up to be with her husba
