t get in. So she was extremely Right-wing. Half the essays which I had to write were not even on the syl
labus, and the year after me, everybody doing PPE got a Third, so they realised that something was wrong. So I got a very very bad degree. I found that the course, the PPE course, was pathetic. But I had an amazing group of contemporaries, many of whom ha
