\par Judith:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid4982948\charrsid4982948 Oh gosh, you\rquote ve been doing 
your homework! (LAUGHS) Oh God! (LAUGHS) Oh my God! Well, I went on a one or two week skiing holiday through the university thing, and I went off to Austria, and it was all for students, and then I met up all these French students \endash 
 I was the only English person there. And I met up with this guy I called \'93Hubert\'94, who was at the L\rquote 
Ecole Normale Superieure, which is where Sartre and de Beauvoir went, and that was literally down the road from my hostel. Funnily enough, I think I was drawn to him because, I fo
und him totally unattractive, but he was an intellectual. Then he and I, and two other guys at the L\rquote Ecole Normale, they said, \'93Let\rquote s drive to the Mediterranean\'94
. So we all went off there, and we stayed in separate rooms, although the other two guys kept thinking that Hubert and I were a couple, we weren\rquote t. And they locked us in a bedroom once at one point, and of course, they thought I couldn\rquote 
t understand French properly, and they would refer to me as \'93la b\'eate\'94 \endash  \'93the fool\'94. And then Hubert wanted to go to La Rochelle or something, Hubert wanted to take the boat over to the island, and I said I didn\rquote 
t want to go, because that was when we hitch-hiked to Normandy or Brittany, or something. It\rquote s all lost in time, but I remember him insisting that I had to go to the island off La Rochelle, and I said I didn\rquote t want to go, and then I said, 
\'93La b\'eate\'94 - \'93The fool has learnt to say no\'94. And he was quite shocked, he said, \'93God, you know you were called \lquote la b\'eate?\rquote \'94 In the end, I don\rquote t know how it was, I got to know thi
s young woman in a hostel or something, a French woman, and we hitch-hiked back together to Paris. But he didn\rquote t feature much, I just thought I was going to, one day, meet my soul mate. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
\b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid4982948\charrsid4982948 
