\par Judith:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid4982948\charrsid4982948 No, no. I said he wasn\rquote t my soul mate, but I was in awe of him, because they knew everything, you know. Mind you, they didn
\rquote t know anything about modern life, they just knew they could quote mediaeval poetry and this, that, and the other. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid4982948\charrsid4982948 
