\par Judith:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid4982948\charrsid4982948 October, \rquote 61. I left school in \rquote 
59. I left school and then I went to the Sorbonne and I had a year, then I came back the next autumn to do my Entrance to Oxford, so \rquote 59-\rquote 60, \rquote 60-\rquote 61, so the autumn of \rquote 61 I go to Oxford. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 
