\par Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid4982948\charrsid4982948 Oh. So did you become an activist? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
