\par Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid4982948\charrsid4982948 Interesting. You didn\rquote t, I think, tell me whether you had any really significant tutors or lecturers. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 
\ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid4982948\charrsid4982948 
