s the other trick I don\rquote t like, is in his CV, on the back of his books, it says, \'93Hugh Brody lectured in anthropology at Belfast\'94. He was registered for a degree in Sociology, and he was lecturing in the Philosophy Department. I don\rquote 
t think he\rquote d read a single anthropology book at the time! But that\rquote s the only permanent job he\rquote s ever had! Yes! A one-year lectureship at Belfast! }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
