Yes, because we had two hours a week with Leach, just five of us, and the whole course, that was the only course for post-grads. Otherwise we had to do all the courses, select courses that were given to undergrads, like \'93Religion and Ritual\'94, or 
\'93Economics and whatever\'94. Now, there were the mentors \endash  I\rquote ve just realised. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid4982948\charrsid4982948 
