ising alumni, and I got some phone calls a couple of years ago, you know, these young women, and I told the story. I just said, \'93I was devastated. I was paying them money. I never entered the place again. And I went away sobbing\'94
. And, of course, they were all very sweet, and in the end they persuaded me to give some money. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid4982948\charrsid4982948 
