 Malcolm McLeod \endash  and I begged if he would tutor me, and he did, and he was brilliant. Now, he was somebody, he just said, \'93Judith, your essays are fantastic!\'94 You know, \'93You\rquote ve got to go on with anthropology. These are brilliant!
\'94 That was another who was my contemporary. I\rquote ve since interviewed him for my book, and we got to know each other again when he came up to be Curator in Glasgow, the Hunterian Museum, and he wrote references for me. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 
