 that was provided by the Local Authority. Of course, I\rquote ve got all my lovely handwritten field notes, and I\rquote m going to donate them to Newnham College, and I\rquote ve just got, in press, an article, it\rquote 
s part of a thing in celebration of a wonderful German professor \endash  Bernard Strech (?? sp \endash  13.39). He\rquote s organised big research projects on gypsies throughout Europe, he was at 
