d come in through an agent and an Authority, and you wanted to do something with them, maybe on their side. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid4982948\charrsid4982948 
