y presentation as well, that we can\rquote t say that they all could explain their customs because they came from India. It\rquote s all wrong, anyway, because even now, a social worker told me, a year ago, \'93Oh, gypsies burn their caravans because that
\rquote s Hinduism\'94. I said, \'93Gypsies never burn the bodies of the dead. They never cremate, and yet Hindu cremate, I\rquote m sorry\'94. And then the answer was, \'93Well, they\rquote ve forgotten\'94. You know, if it doesn\rquote t fit, \'93They
\rquote ve forgotten\'94. So arrogant! Anyhow, I\rquote ve gone off at a tangent. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid4982948\charrsid4982948 
