 Malcolm did, when I was living on the gypsy camp. I can\rquote t remember whether it was the following year or not, I registered for a B.Litt. at Oxford, and Malcolm gave me a wonderful reference. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
