That was where he made this very clever move. He discovered I had a relationship with Alan, who was lecturer at Edinburgh, so he rang me up and said that, \'93We could make a transfer\'94. Because I\rquote d been interviewed, and runner up fo
r the Chair which he\rquote d got, the Principal \endash  which is what they\rquote re called in Edinburgh \endash  was delighted to agree to my transfer, because he saw how I\rquote 
d performed at the interview. But there had to be a deal, because Joan Busfield had to negotiate with Martin Harris that there would be a replacement. I went to the AUT, because Cohen was not politically sophisticated, because he said, \'93
Just go to Martin Harris and say you want to leave\'94. And I rang up the AUT, and they said, \'93That\rquote s a disaster, because they\rquote ll think you\rquote 
re no good. You need the Principal of Edinburgh to ring the Vice-Chancellor at Essex, saying, \lquote I want Okely\rquote \'94
. And the Principal, having seen me at the interview that year, rang up Martin Harris, and then there was this incredible emergency Staff Meeting with all the sociologists, and Mary McIntosh was bewildered, because she said, \'93
Martin Harris said that the Principal of Edinburgh says, \lquote I want Okely on a transfer\rquote \'94. There were jokes about football, and only a few months before, she\rquote d told me I wasn\rquote 
t to be considered even for a senior lecturership. And she wrote me a sort of dreadful little creepy note about how sorry she was to leave me, I asked a post-grad. to read it for me, because I said, \'93I\rquote ve no confidence in this woman\'94
. But anyway, so I
 went to Edinburgh, and that was when I was given a lot more opportunity to teach first year undergrads., because it was anthropology. Also eventually they had an MA in Social Science, and I was allowed to run an entire course on ethnographic methods. So 
I did an entire course. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid4982948\charrsid4982948 
