\rquote s going to a bloody boarding school\'94. ... I was trying to wr
ite up my thesis while they would come at weekends, total chaos! But anyway, she moved into the house, and I was at Durham, and I realised, within ten days, it was a disaster. ... Well, I\rquote 
m just saying that life became impossible. And the next week, I met Alan at a conference. I just said, \'93Laura\rquote s got to go. It\rquote s unmanageable\'94. Life had become impossible, and I met Alan, and, you know, that was it. ... }{\rtlch\fcs1 
