\par Judith:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid4982948\charrsid4982948 Yes. Yes. It was believed that they had died out, and then suddenly somebody recorded that there were some Wiyampi in Brazil \endash 
 there had been some on the border \endash  and Peter Riviere (?? \endash 
 sp. 39.44) was his supervisor, and Peter got a big grant for Alan to go off and do work there. And, you know, Alan was brilliant. But we had huge intellectual arguments. He was obsessed about, \'93We mustn\rquote t have categories. We mustn\rquote 
t have classification\'94. And he was vitriolic about Levi-Strauss and vitriolic about psychoanalysis. He\rquote d had a very very traumatic childhood \endash  which I won\rquote 
t go into ... But in the end, I put my flat on the market, and I bought a house in the suburbs of Edinburgh. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid4982948\charrsid4982948 
