\par Judith:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid4982948\charrsid4982948 I know, well, that\rquote s it, I don\rquote t think I ever switch off. I was interv
iewed by a young woman about work/life balance, and I said, \'93I hate this term, because I never switch off, as an intellectual my mind is going all the time\'94. I rented a cottage in Essex last year, so I could go walking, but, unfortunately, I\rquote 
ve now got a spinal injury so I can\rquote t walk very far. I\rquote m hoping it\rquote ll get better, but I don\rquote 
t know. I like socialising. I have a wonderful set of friends here. We can go out to the theatre or whatever, so I do that. I listen to music, I watch a fair amount of television, but as I said, I socialise, and there\rquote 
s always things to do in Oxford, whether it\rquote s work or not. I have invitations - four years ago I was in Taiwan, I said it\rquote s work, but it\rquote s also fun. Because if you\rquote re invited to these places, you\rquote re not going as a si
ngle traveller. I have been on holiday with a lovely friend, by the way \endash 
 she and I met when we were at the College - my last job before I went to Cambridge, was lecturing at the College of Further Education here, which was the High School where T.E. Lawrence studied. I lectured there. And Ros \endash I\rquote 
m Godmother to her son \endash  her husband is very very ill, and he can\rquote t fly, so we would go off on SAGA Holidays, because she\rquote s got problems with health, but we\rquote ve been to South Africa, we went to Cuba, and we went to 
Namibia for two or three weeks andthat was absolutely stunning. You know you\rquote re in safe hands. It was very very moving, of course, going to South Africa. And my sister, the night before I went, sent me the addresses of where we\rquote 
d lived as a child, and I actually got the coach to drive down one of the streets where I had once lived. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid4982948\charrsid4982948 
